author: Bethesda Softworks
description:
Keep the Fallout Day celebrations going with this pair of achievement-friendly Creations by KaoruSatou!

🍽️ Cosmic Diner: 1950s diner themed furniture for your outposts and ships, including items with Nuka-Cola themes! https://beth.games/4qpQYgd
🛋️ Commonwealth Furniture Pack: Adds a selection of Fallout 4-inspired furniture for your outposts and ships. https://beth.games/4qsh0iL
title: Decorate your ship or outpost with this pair of Fallout-inspired Starfield Creations by KaoruSatou!
